latestIgtvVideos.title: Dewy Glowy look with unicorn eyes🦄!
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
I love how this look has turned out. A tip to share with you guys, if you are creating some dewy/Glowy look make use of creamy or liquid based products instead of using powdery products( such as check tint instead of powder based blush.) Also use a little more highlighter to get that glowy finish.
Products used:
Myglamm Clean Beauty Argan Oil BB Foundation Stick in the shade -oak
Myglamm Perfect Curves Matte Lip Crayon -Terra
Myglamm Manish Malhotra 9 in 1 eyeshadow palette in the shade -Reverie 
Myglamm Manish Malhotra Mascara
Myglamm Manish Malhotra Glitter Eyeliner in the shade -Dazzle
Myglamm Clean Beauty Cocoa Butter Lip and Cheek Pencil in the shade -French Rose
Myglamm K.play Flavoured Highlighter -Pink Rose
Myglamm LIT Matte Lipliner Pencil in the shade -Sass
